It's all right, Simon.
Give it to me.

1802
01:52:55,476 --> 01:52:56,560
Uh-uh.

1803
01:53:02,775 --> 01:53:05,319
Listen to me.

1804
01:53:05,486 --> 01:53:06,529
We can make it.

1805
01:53:06,696 --> 01:53:09,407
We've got to go now,
and we've got to be strong.

1806
