I am sorry you have become so wealthy.

1810
01:54:49,924 --> 01:54:51,509
Ah, nothing I can't fix.

1811
01:54:51,675 --> 01:54:53,427
We might just keep some.

1812
01:54:54,095 --> 01:54:55,096
Come on.

1813
01:54:58,933 --> 01:55:00,643
They will arrest me now?

1814
01:55:01,185 --> 01:55:02,186
No.

1815
01:55:03,562 --> 01:55:06,107
So long as you settle her affairs honestly

1816
01:55:06,732 --> 01:55:08,859
and pay back what you owe.

1817
01:55:17,535 --> 01:55:19,078
You return to London, Doctor?

1818
01:55:19,495 --> 01:55:21,956
There's nothing for me in London anymore.

1819
01:55:22,665 --> 01:55:24,083
West Africa.

1820
01:55:24,250 --> 01:55:25,876
Perhaps I can do some good there.

1821
01:56:05,249 --> 01:56:07,585
I wish I'd never got to see you work.

1822
01:56:14,300 --> 01:56:15,509
Um...

1823
01:56:18,220 --> 01:56:19,513
Perhaps...

1824
01:57:13,359 --> 01:57:14,652
- See you soon, Syd.
- Thanks a lot for tonight.

1825
01:57:14,818 --> 01:57:15,903
See you in a couple days.

1826
01:57:17,154 --> 01:57:19,990
Tell the band one more song,
then they have to finish their rehearsal.

1827
